name: Vintage Stripes
description:
Sometimes simple is better. I wanted to go for a full retro look on this body painting. It was kinda nice to only spend about 20 mins painting the body instead of the usual 3 hours. And nice to see that still leaves a nice emotive effect.

See this series in motion at: https://youtu.be/kQkcbb6Dnz4

model: Coyote
body paint and photography by Roustan (bodypainter.com)
